name: Hidden sides of the soul
description:
The first collector of this NFT will receive this original painting. 1st collector, please DM me via Twitter @Maks_Denysenko 

Hidden sides of the soul
Moving to the original source balances and directs the gaze to the original depths of the practice. Each time, listening to the Tao Te Ching, a new facet opens up, it seems like a long-forgotten key to the hidden sides of the soul appears ...
Quote by Denysenko Andrii

Artwork created by Maksym Denysenko in 2020, 70x40 cm, spray paint on canvas, 1679*2986 pix.
